name: Victoria Sisters
description:
## Victoria Sisters

A Halloween collectible. Increase Pumpkin yield by 20% and summon the necromancer.

To craft this item you must collect 50 Jack-o-lantern's and trade with the travelling salesman.

### Crafting Costs

---

- 50 Jack-o-lantern
